reviewText:
A really funny party game to enjoy with friends and also random people that you meet online (that are really friendly)! I would suggest this game to anybody who like board/card games that also looks anime/cute.

PRO:
-Pretty deep gameplay that could lead to many hours of fun;
-It's also luck based so even if you meet players that have higher level than you there is still a chance to win;
-Many colorful maps, and a lot of missions for singleplayer;
-The soundtracks in this game are amazing;

CONS:
-Could be frustrating at times (depends on your mood too though!);
-The only way to get EXP and unlock more things is by playing online and sometimes you just can't find lobbies (that's where friendships really helps)
